{"type":"video_comment","id":26554,"parentType":"video","parentId":2981,"uid":6112,"contents":"张维为、胡锡进、金灿荣等群狗齐吠:<br>\n<br>\n文曲再世~~盛世可期啊~~~<br>\n<br>\n特出(tè chū)，乃古早非常典雅的高阶词汇，曾巩《回傅权书》「足下之材，可谓特出」。由此看得出今上博士非虚也，学识远逾吾辈，含金量之高，深不可测，佩服！佩服！<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LWSlYgM.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LWSlYgM.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LWSlYgM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n混殽(hùn yáo)，古文中的\"殽\" ，同“淆”，吴筠《览古》诗之二：「忠诚及狙诈，殽混安可甄?」足见此系惊世骇俗的孤高用法，常吾等朽才能引据，讲究！讲究！<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/pZ0KmBO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pZ0KmBO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/pZ0KmBO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-09-09","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}